"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-olympics-viewers-stunned-woman-flashes-tennis-match-21339814\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympicsviewers were left stunned after a woman flashed the camera during a tennis match.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 89, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident occurred during the women's singles quarter-final betweenIga Swiatekand Danielle Collins on Wednesday night.\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Danielle Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danielle_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators in the arena were performing a Mexican wave during a break in play between the two players.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\", \"score\": 0.9999990027015854, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mexican wave\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wave_(audience)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  The camera then stopped a man, woman and child, who were sat in the stands.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All three smiled and waved to the camera before the woman lifted up her top to show her bikini.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fan who saw the footage on X wrote: 'Having a nice family outing at the Olympics and then Mum had to show her boobs again.'\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another user wrote: 'Bizarre behaviour with a young child.'\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 72