\": 2.158872697267455e-06, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American, Collins, who stopped playing in the third set because of an injured stomach muscle, retired from the match, handing the victory to Swiatek.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.99980882935352, \"rank\": 9.707918943633864e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"score\": 0.999997840908293, \"rank\": 2.158872697267455e-06, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told Iga she did not have to be insincere about, you know, my injury,' Collins said.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1295, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.277241144616806e-13, \"text\": \"Iga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iga_Province\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"score\": 0.999997840908293, \"rank\": 2.158872697267455e-06, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HarperCollins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is a lot that happens on camera, and there are a lot of people with a ton of charisma and come out and are one way on camera and another way in the locker room.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And I just have not had the best experience, and I do not really feel like anybody needs to be insincere.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They can be the way that they are.\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can accept that, and I do not need the fakeness.'\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Imane Khelif fires warning to Olympic opponents after making boxer quit  ArrowMORE:The internet is going to extreme lengths to date Paris 2024 athletes  ArrowMORE:Why USA think they are top of the Olympics medal table - when they are not  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to